<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">国风·邶风·新台</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonf897b4aa44f3">
新台有泚，河水弥弥。燕婉之求，蘧篨不鲜。<br />新台有洒，河水浼浼。燕婉之求，蘧篨不殄。<br />鱼网之设，鸿则离之。燕婉之求，得此戚施。
</div>
</div>
